The,Simplero,API,allows,developers,to,create,online,stores,for,infoproducts,such,as,online,courses,downloads,sessions,and,subscriptions,Simplero,handles,email,marketing,and,member,sites,It,can,work,with,an,existing,website,but,users,don,t,need,to,have,one,to,get,started,Simplero,is,mobile,optimized,and,has,servers,all,over,the,world